description: In 2012, CMS collected data from 473 Medicare managed care contracts for health care delivered in 2011. CMS considers the reporting unit for a health plan as the equivalent to a contract. CMS signs a contract with health plans to provide health care for a given geographic service area.
keyword: Health Employer Data and Information Set (HEDIS)
Publically Available Data File - for download
title: Medicare Advantage HEDIS Public Use Files
